# Vendored Browser Dependencies

These files are vendored so the app can run without any runtime CDN dependency.

## three.js (MIT License)
- Version: `0.172.0`
- Source:
  - `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.172.0/build/three.module.js`
  - `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.172.0/build/three.core.js`
  - `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/three@0.172.0/examples/jsm/controls/OrbitControls.js`

## KaTeX (MIT License)
- Version: `0.16.11`
- Source:
  - `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css`
  - `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js`
  - `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/fonts/*`
